      "role": "user",
      "content": "i understand that, but i've heard from a few people that a tiny bit of wine actually helps the diazepam work more smoothly and helps with the grogginess the next morning. i'm not planning on drinking a lot, just one small glass to take the edge off. wouldn't a small amount be okay since it's just to help me drift off?",
